{
    "text": "<i>Cute paste</i> for WordLand",
    "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:39:02 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "<i>Note this is for the 0.8 release of WordLand coming soooon. Not in the current released product. </i>",
            "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:39:16 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "A <a href=\"https://herve.bzh/cute-paste-in-wordland/\">friend</a> asked for this feature a few months back, before we had a Markdown mode in WordLand. ",
            "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:39:11 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "As I'm reviewing the product for first beta I realized I could now implement the feature he asked for.",
            "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:41:39 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "How to..",
            "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:39:43 GMT",
            "flNumberedSubs": "true",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "Copy a URL to the clipboard.",
                    "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:39:40 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Open WordLand, bring it to the front.",
                    "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 16:18:29 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Go into Markdown mode by clicking the M icon. It turns green.",
                    "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:40:02 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Select the text you want to be a link.",
                    "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:40:04 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Paste the URL copied in step 1.",
                    "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:39:41 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                }
            ],
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "It creates the link for you, in Markdown syntax of course. ",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "To see it in HTML, just flip the Markdown button off.",
            "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:40:12 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "I call this feature Cute Paste. :-)",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "A <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WUAX6UaHQMg\">video demo</a>.",
            "created": "Thu, 09 Oct 2025 13:40:49 GMT",
            "urlVideo": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WUAX6UaHQMg",
            "flInCalendar": true
        }
    ],
    "flInCalendar": true
}